---
import { u } from '../lib/url';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
// TODO: paste the Google Form URL here when ready.
const FORM_URL = 'https://forms.gle/REPLACE-WITH-YOUR-FORM';
---
<BaseLayout title="Join · BASIS">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h1>Join</h1>

    <p>
      We're a small group, about a dozen members, six or seven attending each session.
      We can comfortably grow to ~25 in the wider group and ~12 at any one meeting.
      We add people slowly and deliberately.
    </p>

    <h2>What we look for</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>You read papers cover-to-cover, not abstracts.</li>
      <li>You can show up in Bangalore every three weeks.</li>
      <li>You'd enjoy playing a role (e.g. Contrarian, Bridge Builder) and prepping for it.</li>
      <li>You're more curious than performative.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How to apply</h2>
    <p>
      Fill the form. We'll read it. If it feels like a fit, we'll invite you to a session.
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href={FORM_URL} rel="noopener" style="font-size:1.1rem;">→ Application form</a>
    </p>

    <h2>If you're not sure yet</h2>
    <p>
      Browse the <a href={u("/sessions")}>sessions</a> and <a href={u("/papers")}>papers</a>.
      If a session has notes marked <em>pending</em>, you can also contribute notes
      yourself as a way of introducing your thinking, see <a href={u("/contribute")}>contribute</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
